#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:2
#: 091b13c086414d77986d9568d81a1290
msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:4
#: 2e06001fa4d540659fdc4dd28fdde8ed
msgid "本指南会带你完成一次最小可用的播放流程：创建播放器、加载音频、播放、暂停和调整音量。 开始前请先完成 :doc:`installation`。"
msgstr ""
"This guide walks you through the smallest useful playback flow: create a "
"player, load audio, play it, pause it, and adjust the volume. Complete "
":doc:`installation` before starting."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:8
#: 8d6f3ebe77284dee9e6156bc56c61e47
msgid "你需要知道的三个概念"
msgstr "Three Concepts You Need to Know"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:13
#: f076c72925a243d0ab7e3fbb8ec545ac
msgid "名称"
msgstr "Name"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:14
#: 979e279746ab43a18b9c5dfdf82af8f9
msgid "作用"
msgstr "Role"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:15
#: cb47febd7db04a22a0ee4544032c2a64
msgid "``FmodAudioStreamPlayer``"
msgstr "``FmodAudioStreamPlayer``"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:16
#: 5319d912dcca4da0a5f5810308c2efca
msgid "场景中的播放节点，适合播放背景音乐、环境音和普通 2D 声音。"
msgstr ""
"A playback node in the scene, suitable for background music, ambience, "
"and regular 2D sounds."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:17
#: 94d3c1745bfb496dbf3df740a27f677d
msgid "``FmodAudioStream``"
msgstr "``FmodAudioStream``"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:18
#: f095937dbe834e4793ccd73f682db249
msgid "FMOD 音频资源，保存音频数据和加载模式。"
msgstr "An FMOD audio resource that stores audio data and its loading mode."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:19
#: 46597e841df244ea948f4490e6632875
msgid "``FmodServer``"
msgstr "``FmodServer``"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:20
#: 57021f804cd145889cc31bfceaba6062
msgid "全局 FMOD 系统入口，用于访问主系统、主通道组和性能数据。"
msgstr ""
"The global entry point for the FMOD system. Use it to access the main "
"system, master channel group, and performance data."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:24
#: ef0c50a0be154419a8b72149cbca41b6
msgid ""
"如果只是播放一段音乐，通常只需要 ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer`` 和 "
"``FmodAudioStream``。``FmodSystem``、``FmodChannel``、``FmodDSP`` 等底层对象 "
"可以等到需要混音、DSP 或更细控制时再学习。"
msgstr ""
"If you only want to play a piece of music, you usually only need "
"``FmodAudioStreamPlayer`` and ``FmodAudioStream``. Lower-level objects "
"such as ``FmodSystem``, ``FmodChannel``, and ``FmodDSP`` can wait until "
"you need mixing, DSP, or finer control."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:29
#: f60048c63a8043798311cea012ec9d3d
msgid "在编辑器中播放第一段音频"
msgstr "Play Your First Audio in the Editor"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:32
#: 611f4137b42644a9aa692aca55cf581c
msgid "创建场景"
msgstr "Create a Scene"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:34
#: 8d678b928433445caf65b567fd172e31
msgid "新建一个 Godot 场景。"
msgstr "Create a new Godot scene."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:35
#: 488310bba0b14c659ff84ef0ffd5e74d
msgid "添加一个 ``Node`` 作为根节点。"
msgstr "Add a ``Node`` as the root node."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:36
#: a0402e4467cf4ada956c8927d80e8115
msgid "添加一个 ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer`` 子节点。"
msgstr "Add a ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer`` child node."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:37
#: 293292fe33714ffb89a2e56c56ef0b37
msgid "保存场景，例如 ``main.tscn``。"
msgstr "Save the scene, for example as ``main.tscn``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:40
#: 75d00c1954814782a8f1dd87ab95b01a
msgid "导入音频"
msgstr "Import Audio"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:42
#: 94f4b09ccb4445dfbe56d86f2f86bf31
msgid "将音频文件放入项目目录，例如 ``res://music/background.mp3``。"
msgstr ""
"Place an audio file in the project, for example "
"``res://music/background.mp3``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:43
#: ed1fcfbaf6d44124993bd162e61ede8d
msgid "在 Godot 的 **导入** 面板中，将导入类型设置为 **FMOD Audio**。"
msgstr "In Godot's **Import** panel, set the import type to **FMOD Audio**."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:44
#: e426cc8bec4348629e173101da194dc5
msgid "根据用途选择导入预设："
msgstr "Choose an import preset based on how the audio will be used:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:46
#: 26473e8396124f6daca705bd818c7bbd
msgid "**Stream (Low memory)**：适合背景音乐和较长音频。"
msgstr "**Stream (Low memory)**: suitable for background music and longer audio."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:47
#: fd4f4a7882054c2baaa243099b96e831
msgid "**Sample (High quality)**：适合短音效和需要低延迟的声音。"
msgstr ""
"**Sample (High quality)**: suitable for short sound effects and sounds "
"that need low latency."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:48
#: 6279911ac9534a38b7b282c5063845ee
msgid "**Loop Sample**：适合需要循环播放的短音效。"
msgstr "**Loop Sample**: suitable for short sound effects that need to loop."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:50
#: c13c06fa5b8a4e86bf2263b91b4309ff
msgid "点击 **重新导入**。"
msgstr "Click **Reimport**."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:53
#: b16e3bb53c1d4fdca83a452eb605fc6e
msgid "播放音频"
msgstr "Play Audio"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:55
#: 742e76e84abb4e8ba21988561fb7afec
msgid "选中 ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer`` 节点。"
msgstr "Select the ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer`` node."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:56
#: 4e59ada6c3d54d18b2a9adb080a27fda
msgid "在 Inspector 中，将导入后的 ``FmodAudioStream`` 资源设置到 ``Stream`` 属性。"
msgstr ""
"In the Inspector, assign the imported ``FmodAudioStream`` resource to the"
" ``Stream`` property."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:57
#: 47bfe37f00644cb787818527dd287c7b
msgid "勾选 ``Playing``，或启用 ``Auto Play`` 让它进入场景树时自动播放。"
msgstr ""
"Enable ``Playing``, or enable ``Auto Play`` so it starts when it enters "
"the scene tree."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:59
#: ea6cd0b36de643da96718c32b51536c1
msgid "如果听不到声音，请先确认 FMOD 运行库已放入插件目录，并查看 Godot 输出面板是否有 GDExtension 或 FMOD 初始化错误。"
msgstr ""
"If you cannot hear anything, first make sure the FMOD runtime library is "
"in the plugin directory, and check Godot's Output panel for GDExtension "
"or FMOD initialization errors."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:63
#: f873b492b7444ee781d66e007685eb83
msgid "用代码加载并播放"
msgstr "Load and Play from Code"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:65
#: 2eadf8c76e874b98b16f497d43aec320
msgid "如果不想通过导入器创建资源，也可以直接从路径加载音频文件。"
msgstr ""
"If you do not want to create a resource through the importer, you can "
"also load an audio file directly from a path."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:67
#: 4f818828838545aab9f277a339b160b8
msgid ""
"extends Node\n"
"\n"
"@onready var player: FmodAudioStreamPlayer = $FmodAudioStreamPlayer\n"
"\n"
"func _ready() -> void:\n"
"    var stream := FmodAudioStream.load_from_file(\n"
"        \"res://music/background.mp3\",\n"
"        FmodAudioStream.MODE_STREAM | FmodAudioStream.MODE_LOOP\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    if stream == null:\n"
"        push_error(\"Failed to load audio file\")\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    player.stream = stream\n"
"    player.play()"
msgstr ""
"extends Node\n"
"\n"
"@onready var player: FmodAudioStreamPlayer = $FmodAudioStreamPlayer\n"
"\n"
"func _ready() -> void:\n"
"    var stream := FmodAudioStream.load_from_file(\n"
"        \"res://music/background.mp3\",\n"
"        FmodAudioStream.MODE_STREAM | FmodAudioStream.MODE_LOOP\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    if stream == null:\n"
"        push_error(\"Failed to load audio file\")\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    player.stream = stream\n"
"    player.play()"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:86
#: ae316eb0a9794b6b99787c88df735eef
msgid ""
"``MODE_STREAM`` 适合长音频；``MODE_LOOP`` 会让音频循环播放。短音效通常更适合使用 "
"``MODE_SAMPLE``，可以降低频繁触发时的播放延迟。"
msgstr ""
"``MODE_STREAM`` is suitable for long audio. ``MODE_LOOP`` makes the audio"
" loop. Short sound effects are usually better with ``MODE_SAMPLE``, which"
" can reduce latency when triggered frequently."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:90
#: cc99087722c9420eb0f2b742185582d3
msgid "控制播放"
msgstr "Control Playback"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:92
#: a0af3d13884e468a8c3c669175dd121b
msgid "下面的示例使用键盘控制播放、暂停和音量。你可以把脚本挂到场景根节点上。"
msgstr ""
"The following example uses the keyboard to control playback, pause, and "
"volume. You can attach the script to the scene root node."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:94
#: 3425dc4710c64059a43388bfb29f54a4
msgid ""
"extends Node\n"
"\n"
"@onready var player: FmodAudioStreamPlayer = $FmodAudioStreamPlayer\n"
"\n"
"func _unhandled_input(event: InputEvent) -> void:\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_accept\"):\n"
"        player.playing = not player.playing\n"
"\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_cancel\"):\n"
"        player.stream_paused = not player.stream_paused\n"
"\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_up\"):\n"
"        player.volume_db += 3.0\n"
"\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_down\"):\n"
"        player.volume_db -= 3.0"
msgstr ""
"extends Node\n"
"\n"
"@onready var player: FmodAudioStreamPlayer = $FmodAudioStreamPlayer\n"
"\n"
"func _unhandled_input(event: InputEvent) -> void:\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_accept\"):\n"
"        player.playing = not player.playing\n"
"\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_cancel\"):\n"
"        player.stream_paused = not player.stream_paused\n"
"\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_up\"):\n"
"        player.volume_db += 3.0\n"
"\n"
"    if event.is_action_pressed(\"ui_down\"):\n"
"        player.volume_db -= 3.0"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:114
#: cf913d6881b74e798414f2877ec45da1
msgid "常用属性"
msgstr "Common Properties"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:119
#: 1c0166414c614e01966109b23ca745fe
msgid "属性"
msgstr "Property"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:120
