msgid "输出到指定音频总线，默认是 ``Master``。"
msgstr "Outputs to the specified audio bus. The default is ``Master``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:135
#: 185d993fc5824cda9b161a4c5861ce96
msgid "播放一次性音效"
msgstr "Play a One-Shot Sound Effect"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:137
#: 9f187314780b41bcad31eb35ba4db56a
msgid "如果只是播放一个短音效，也可以直接通过 ``FmodSystem`` 创建声音并播放。"
msgstr ""
"If you only need to play a short sound effect, you can also create and "
"play a sound directly through ``FmodSystem``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:139
#: f55d9a82741e4fd9b7d0ce0b3b42b228
msgid ""
"func play_click_sound() -> void:\n"
"    var system: FmodSystem = FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var sound: FmodSound = system.create_sound_from_file(\n"
"        \"res://sfx/click.wav\",\n"
"        FmodSystem.FMOD_MODE_CREATESAMPLE\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    if sound == null:\n"
"        push_error(\"Failed to load sound\")\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    var master: FmodChannelGroup = system.get_master_channel_group()\n"
"    system.play_sound(sound, master, false)"
msgstr ""
"func play_click_sound() -> void:\n"
"    var system: FmodSystem = FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var sound: FmodSound = system.create_sound_from_file(\n"
"        \"res://sfx/click.wav\",\n"
"        FmodSystem.FMOD_MODE_CREATESAMPLE\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    if sound == null:\n"
"        push_error(\"Failed to load sound\")\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    var master: FmodChannelGroup = system.get_master_channel_group()\n"
"    system.play_sound(sound, master, false)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:155
#: e25d2425a400423c9443ffd060e6f52f
msgid ""
"需要频繁播放同一个音效时，建议提前加载并复用 ``FmodAudioStream`` 或 ``FmodSound``， "
"不要每次按键都重新从文件读取。"
msgstr ""
"If you need to play the same sound effect frequently, preload and reuse "
"``FmodAudioStream`` or ``FmodSound`` instead of reading the file again on"
" every input event."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:159
#: 5be0909e0b3b48de85523f116406d410
msgid "添加一个简单 DSP 效果"
msgstr "Add a Simple DSP Effect"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:161
#: dbea5d9f242b45d29e8f65e8bba3b9b8
msgid "下面的示例把混响添加到主通道组。这样所有经过主输出的声音都会带有混响。"
msgstr ""
"The following example adds reverb to the master channel group. All sounds"
" that pass through the main output will have reverb."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:163
#: 75ccd5749e3c4a91b55f1ebb27061eaa
msgid ""
"func add_reverb_to_master() -> void:\n"
"    var system: FmodSystem = FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var reverb: FmodDSP = "
"system.create_dsp_by_type(FmodDSP.DSP_TYPE_SFXREVERB)\n"
"\n"
"    if reverb == null:\n"
"        push_error(\"Failed to create reverb DSP\")\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    var master: FmodChannelGroup = system.get_master_channel_group()\n"
"    master.add_dsp(-1, reverb)"
msgstr ""
"func add_reverb_to_master() -> void:\n"
"    var system: FmodSystem = FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var reverb: FmodDSP = "
"system.create_dsp_by_type(FmodDSP.DSP_TYPE_SFXREVERB)\n"
"\n"
"    if reverb == null:\n"
"        push_error(\"Failed to create reverb DSP\")\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    var master: FmodChannelGroup = system.get_master_channel_group()\n"
"    master.add_dsp(-1, reverb)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:178
#: 1d92b9a7548e475ab4e3fd79c04d227e
msgid "``-1`` 表示把 DSP 添加到链末尾。实际项目中更推荐把效果添加到具体总线或通道组， 避免影响所有声音。"
msgstr ""
"``-1`` means adding the DSP to the end of the chain. In real projects, it"
" is usually better to add effects to a specific bus or channel group so "
"they do not affect every sound."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:182
#: 3cb27cb299ec4cd4a819f3b3447afce2
msgid "查看性能数据"
msgstr "View Performance Data"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:184
#: 9b8c26e6af654f2488dbce36cbcbd0e7
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 会把 FMOD 性能数据注册到 Godot 的性能监视器中。运行项目后， 可以在 **调试器 > 监视器** "
"中查看 ``FmodCPUUsage`` 和 ``FmodFileUsage`` 相关指标。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer registers FMOD performance data in Godot's performance "
"monitors. After running the project, you can view ``FmodCPUUsage`` and "
"``FmodFileUsage`` metrics in **Debugger > Monitors**."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:187
#: a7fc80911c034d7585954e4537fe8b75
msgid "也可以在代码中读取："
msgstr "You can also read them from code:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:189
#: e40818c633794a14aab6b4eaacba4d25
#, python-format
msgid ""
"func _process(_delta: float) -> void:\n"
"    var system: FmodSystem = FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var cpu_usage: Dictionary = system.get_cpu_usage()\n"
"    var channels: Dictionary = system.get_channels_playing()\n"
"\n"
"    print(\"DSP CPU: %.2f%%\" % cpu_usage[\"dsp\"])\n"
"    print(\"Real channels: %d\" % channels[\"real_channels\"])"
msgstr ""
"func _process(_delta: float) -> void:\n"
"    var system: FmodSystem = FmodServer.get_main_system()\n"
"    var cpu_usage: Dictionary = system.get_cpu_usage()\n"
"    var channels: Dictionary = system.get_channels_playing()\n"
"\n"
"    print(\"DSP CPU: %.2f%%\" % cpu_usage[\"dsp\"])\n"
"    print(\"Real channels: %d\" % channels[\"real_channels\"])"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:200
#: 2a78048e6181436981f7bf05decc8588
msgid "下一步"
msgstr "Next Steps"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:202
#: 4e1b2eab250c4edc97baa4105f36cae1
msgid ""
"阅读 :doc:`../user_guide/audio_resources`，了解 ``MODE_STREAM`` 和 "
"``MODE_SAMPLE`` 的选择。"
msgstr ""
"Read :doc:`../user_guide/audio_resources` to understand when to choose "
"``MODE_STREAM`` or ``MODE_SAMPLE``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quick_start.rst:203
#: e4f85f2c71f24ed98404f5bdc9ba2551
msgid "阅读 :doc:`../user_guide/playback`，学习播放、暂停、跳转和通道控制。"
msgstr ""
"Read :doc:`../user_guide/playback` to learn playback, pause, seeking, and"
" channel control."

